    <user>anag_factory</user>
    <comment>- Require ocaml-rpm-macros in build for generation of dependencies.
- Now we no longer need the explicit rocq-devel runtime dependency.
</comment>
    <requestid>1343992</requestid>
  </revision>
</revisionlist>
